<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Shadoc</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/3068/3068327.png">
    <style>
        .title{
            font-size: 30px;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-shadow: 1px 3px 3px black;
        }
        .title:hover{
          color: white;
          text-shadow: 1px 2px 1px rgb(90, 90, 90);
        }
        .collapse1{
            margin-left: 50px;
        }
        .nav-link{
            margin: 0px 20px;
        }
        td{
            cursor:context-menu;
        }
        .session{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            width:100%;
        }
        .main1{
            flex-basis: 20%;
            background-color: rgb(13, 110, 253);
        }
        .main2{
            margin-left: 30px;
            flex-basis: 80%;
        }
        .contai{
            margin: 100px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="menu">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
            <div class="container-fluid ">
            <a href="/"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3068/3068327.png" alt="" width="60" height="60" class="d-inline-block align-text-top"></a> 
            <a class="title" href="/">ShaDoc</a>
            <div class="collapse1 navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Trang Chủ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/user/admin">Admin</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/user/getMe">Hồ sơ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/huy.hgs/">Hỗ Trợ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse1 navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
                <div class="navbar-nav">
                    <form class="d-flex" action="/search">
                        <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" name="search" placeholder="Nhập tên môn..." aria-label="Search">
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-light" type="submit">Tìm</button>
                      </form>
                    <div class="collapse1 navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavDarkDropdown">
                        <ul class="navbar-nav">
                          <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDarkDropdownMenuLink" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                Tài Khoản
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-light" aria-labelledby="navbarDarkDropdownMenuLink">
                              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/user/getMe">Hồ sơ</a></li>
                              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/user/admin">Admin</a></li>
                              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/auth/login">Đăng nhập</a></li>
                              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/auth/logout">Đăng xuất</a></li>
                            </ul>
                          </li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="contai">
        <%if(error){%>
            <h1 style="color: red">Lỗi: <%= error.message %></h1>
        <%}else{%>
            <h1 style="color: red"></h1>>Lỗi một cái gì đó rồi, tôi sẽ sửa lại nó ngay, xin lỗi bạn !</h1>
        <%}%>
        <p>Chú ý:</p>
        <p>Lỗi có thể là do trang web đang được cập nhật.</p>
        <p>Bạn có thể chọn chức năng hỗ trợ để được xử lí trong thời gian sớm nhất.</p>
        <a href="#"><button type="reset" class="btn btn-warning">Hỗ trợ ngay</button></a>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-7+zCNj/IqJ95wo16oMtfsKbZ9ccEh31eOz1HGyDuCQ6wgnyJNSYdrPa03rtR1zdB" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-QJHtvGhmr9XOIpI6YVutG+2QOK9T+ZnN4kzFN1RtK3zEFEIsxhlmWl5/YESvpZ13" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>